---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import SeoPage from "@/components/SeoPage.astro";
---

<BaseLayout>
  <SeoPage slot="head" title="About" description="Learn more about Workflow Boom and our mission" />
  <main>
    <div class="mb-8">
      <a 
        href="/" 
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-lightModeForegroundMuted hover:text-lightModeForeground dark:text-darkModeForegroundMuted dark:hover:text-darkModeForeground no-underline"
      >
        ‚Üê Back to Home
      </a>
      <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-4 mb-6">About Workflow Boom</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="prose prose-sm max-w-none text-lightModeForeground dark:text-darkModeForeground">
      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p>
        At Workflow Boom, we specialize in transforming business operations through intelligent automation and streamlined workflows. 
        Our mission is to help businesses eliminate repetitive tasks, reduce human error, and focus on what truly matters - growth and innovation.
      </p>
      
      <h2>What We Do</h2>
      <p>
        We provide comprehensive business automation solutions that include:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>CRM Setup & Optimization</strong> - Streamline your customer relationship management</li>
        <li><strong>Workflow Automation</strong> - Automate repetitive business processes</li>
        <li><strong>Integration Services</strong> - Connect your tools and systems seamlessly</li>
        <li><strong>Process Optimization</strong> - Identify and eliminate bottlenecks in your operations</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2>Why Choose Us</h2>
      <p>
        With years of experience in business process optimization, we understand that every business is unique. 
        Our approach is tailored to your specific needs, ensuring that the solutions we implement actually work for your team and your goals.
      </p>
      
      <h2>Get Started</h2>
      <p>
        Ready to transform your business operations? 
        <a href="/contact" class="text-lightModeCustomLinkBackground dark:text-darkModeCustomLinkBackground hover:underline">Contact us</a> 
        to schedule a consultation and discover how we can help streamline your workflows.
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
